<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 16 at 5:36AM EST  by NWS Cleveland</headline>
<description>...LIGHT SNOW ACCUMULATIONS FOR THE MORNING COMMUTE...
A large area of light snow will move across the region through the
morning commute. Expect to see accumulations of half an inch to
around an inch. Any untreated surfaces will be slippery.</description>
